====================================================


Short description:
    An XACMLv2 fuzzer / testing tool.

Description:
    Create XACMLv2 Requests, send it to an XACML service and display the
    Response, including obligations.

Author:
    Oscar Koeroo

Supported platforms / known to work:
    Ubuntu 12.10
    Debian6
    OSX
    Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5

Requires:
    libxacml, created by Globus; maintained and patch by Nikhef

    Distribution tarbal:
    http://software.nikhef.nl/security/saml2-xacml2-c-lib/xacml-1.0.1.tar.gz

    RPM for RHEL5, RHEL6, fc16, fc17:
    http://software.nikhef.nl/dist/mwsec/rpm/

    source:
    https://ndpfsvn.nikhef.nl/viewvc/mwsec/trunk/saml2-xacml2-c-lib/xacml/

    Requires:
        gsoap
            tested to work with version 2.7.17 and 2.8.8

